OL,3,CHumza Yousaf says police were victims
OL,4,Cin almost a quarter of hate crime
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FPolice officers have been the victims
OL,8,Fof "outrageous abuse" and represent
OL,9,Falmost a quarter of reports under
OL,10,FScotland's new hate crime law, the
OL,11,Ffirst minister said.
OL,13,FHumza Yousaf came under fire again
OL,14,Ffrom the Conservatives over the
OL,15,Flegislation as Tory leader Douglas
OL,16,FRoss said the law, which came into
OL,17,Fforce at the start of April, results
OL,18,Fin police officers being "pulled from
OL,19,Fother parts of the service" to deal
OL,20,Fwith complaints.
