OL,3,CHumza Yousaf says police were victims
OL,4,Cin almost a quarter of hate crime
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FAlmost 9,000 complaints were received
OL,8,Fby Police Scotland in the first two
OL,9,Fweeks of the Act's operation, and Mr
OL,10,FRoss said "40 officers a day have been
OL,11,Fbrought in on overtime" to deal with
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,FRaising the issue during First
OL,15,FMinister's Questions at Holyrood on
OL,16,FThursday, Mr Ross told Mr Yousaf:
OL,17,F"When we opposed the Hate Crime Act,
OL,18,FScottish Conservatives warned the
OL,19,Flegislation would overburden our
OL,20,Falready overstretched police."
