OL,3,CHumza Yousaf says police were victims
OL,4,Cin almost a quarter of hate crime
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FCiting Calum Steele, the general
OL,8,Fsecretary of the International Council
OL,9,Fof Police Representative Associations
OL,10,Fhas branded the law a "hate crime
OL,11,Ffarce".
OL,13,FMr Ross accused the First Minister of
OL,14,Fbeing "unwilling to accept the
OL,15,Ffailures of your Bill and listen to
OL,16,Fthe voice of police officers".
OL,18,FHowever, Mr Yousaf responded: "When it
OL,19,Fcomes to hate crime, almost a quarter
OL,20,Fof the hate crime reports victims are
OL,21,Fpolice officers.
