OL,3,CHumza Yousaf says police were victims
OL,4,Cin almost a quarter of hate crime
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,F"Not only that, from the statistics we
OL,8,Fhave to hand, many of them suffer the
OL,9,Fmost outrageous abuse, some of that
OL,10,Fdirected because of prejudice in
OL,11,Frelation to somebody's sexual
OL,12,Forientation, sometimes in relation to
OL,13,Ftheir race."
OL,15,FWhile legislation was already in place
OL,16,Fagainst stirring up racial hatred, the
OL,17,FHate Crime and Public Order Scotland
OL,18,FAct expanded such protections to other
OL,19,Fgroups, including the elderly, the
OL,20,Fdisabled and LGBT Scots.
