OL,3,CHumza Yousaf says police were victims
OL,4,Cin almost a quarter of hate crime
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FMr Yousaf said "of the 8,984 hate
OL,8,Fcrime complaints that were made to
OL,9,FPolice Scotland in the first couple of
OL,10,Fweeks of April, the vast majority, at
OL,11,Fleast 95%, have been deemed not to be
OL,12,Fcrimes".
OL,14,FPolice Scotland figures show 453 hate
OL,15,Fcrimes were recorded from those
OL,16,Freports ` with 240 in the first week
OL,17,Fthe legislation was in force and 213
OL,18,Fin the second.
