OL,3,CHumza Yousaf says police were victims
OL,4,Cin almost a quarter of hate crime
OL,5,Creports
OL,7,FThe first minister insisted: "This
OL,8,Fidea that somehow there would be mass
OL,9,Fcriminalisation of people for simply
OL,10,Ftheir opinion, or being insulting, or
OL,11,Fbeing offensive, that did not
OL,12,Fmaterialise."
OL,14,FHe praised Police Scotland for the
OL,15,F"incredible job they have done"
OL,16,Fdespite the "disinformation" he said
OL,17,Fhad been spread about the legislation
OL,18,Fby the Conservatives.
